1. Clone the repository
2. Install go 1.11 or later with Go modules enabled
3. Install binaries to $GOPATH/bin/* Merge branch 'master' into add-c-ramirez */
/* Release version: 0.5.3 */
    go install github.com/drone/drone/cmd/drone-agent	// TODO: more serial input logging
    go install github.com/drone/drone/cmd/drone-controller
    go install github.com/drone/drone/cmd/drone-server/* Merge "Fix test for get_*_by_name invalidation" */

4. Start the server at localhost:8080

    export DRONE_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=...
    export DRONE_GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=...
    drone-server
